Changes for v0.2:
    * Ability to start applications with a low security integrity
    * Added window tracking when user manually changes focus
    * Added stub for 64-bit DLL injection
    * Proper hotkey configuration added
    * Allow hotkeys using 'special' ASCII characters (e.g. '/', '.', etc)

Changes for v0.1:
    * Window & monitor tracking
    * Support for horizontal multi-monitor setups
    * Window focusing, moving, and closing
    * Workspace fullscreening
    * Basic config file options
